CASEY BURKHARDT: Great.

00:13:09.920 --> 00:13:11.730
Another great feature of
TalkBack is you can turn it

00:13:11.730 --> 00:13:13.115
off really quickly.

00:13:13.115 --> 00:13:15.620
You go back to the Global
