work correctly.

00:32:02.100 --> 00:32:04.720
So we're good there, and now
if we touch the bar again,

00:32:04.720 --> 00:32:06.980
ANDROID: Bar 5, value
4 highlighted.

00:32:06.980 --> 00:32:07.335
